node.text:
Written and Produced by @_sky_society_ ft. @ehiorobo_ 
Directed by: @nesmithjosh 

OUT NOW via @higherfrequencyrecordings 🌊☁️🏔

“The inspiration for this song was conceived by honoring the union of the Divine Masculine & Feminine Energies coming together as one, opening the portal of creation & guiding the vessel through its daily rituals. This sacred bond within ourselves & with others gives birth to new life & the experiences that we seek to manifest.” - Sky 🎨⛲️🎵

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by EDST 📲 on July 22, 2021 tagging @seandelaneyofficial. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
Team Member Highlight: 

Sean knows the importance of investing in your brand. It doesn’t matter how great your content is if no one is seeing it! 

He says, “Working with EDST has transformed my way of thinking when it comes to promotional strategy. I came onboard with a ton of great content that no one ever got a chance to enjoy. Now I'm getting my music, my brand and my clothing in front of thousands of new eyes daily. I also aquired a new business mindset that I am applying to my marketing moves as a Manager. EDST is an instant game changer for the inspired entrepreneurs ready to change their lives. I am proud to now be among that category.” 

#EDST

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by EDST 📲 on July 21, 2021 tagging @tatianasoleil__. May be an image of one or more people and people standing.

node.text:
“Personal effort- the act of holding yourself accountable for the results you see within your own life. 

EDST is a community of people with an unbelievable hunger for success. As a team we not only motivate each other but also so many musicians, models, and entrepreneurs across the world. 

I’m beyond grateful to be apart of it.” #EDST 

- @tatianasoleil__

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by EDST 📲 on July 20, 2021 tagging @lordofemotion. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text:
Team Member Highlight: 

@lordofemotion is a Community-Based Musician & he’s absolutely killing it on the team! 🔥

He says, “Everyday Success Team or EDST gives you the opportunity to really get non-scamming marketing and makes it simple for you just like they did for myself. Just be sure to listen to your managers like myself and ask about strategies on being intentional with social media as well as your goals in life and whatnot, so you can grow just like I have. EDST is here for you!"

#EDST

node.text:
Huge shoutout to our manager @jeremiah.gvg for completing this milestone and getting his degree ! 🎓 

Now on to bigger and better things 💰

#EDST

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by EDST 📲 on July 18, 2021 tagging @jake__rosenberg. May be an image of 1 person, beard, sunglasses and outdoors.

node.text:
Team Member Highlight: 

Jake is nothing but good vibes & we are so grateful to have him on the team! He’s providing the necessary support & value for his clients to thrive online. 

He says, “it wasn’t until my cousin @jarredrosenberg opened up this new door in my life that has brought nothing but amazing people and amazing opportunities. If I could offer it to everyone I would. Everyday success team has been a blessing in disguise and if I could give any advice, hop on the wagon before it’s too late! Everyday you wait is just one more day your competition gets ahead of you! I love the team I have joined, but more importantly love the family I have gained in the process!”

#EDST

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by EDST 📲 on July 17, 2021 tagging @brandonpatino00. May be an image of 1 person, beard, wrist watch and footwear.

node.text:
Team Member Highlight: 

Brandon is putting in the work EveryDay to level up himself as well as his clients. Let’s show him so love! 🔥 

He says, "Working with EDST has been nothing but a blessing. The community has absolutely transformed my mindset, enhanced my approach to business endeavors, and propelled me much further along my journey than I could have ever imagined. The value you uncover, the people you meet, and the things you learn at EDST consist of nothing but gems."

#EDST

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by EDST 📲 on July 16, 2021 tagging @madisonnhopeee. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text:
Team Member Highlight: 

Madison knows the importance of leveling yourself up! She’s doing an awesome job helping her clients build their brands 🔥

She says, “EDST has a community of people that truly become family🤍 The support system built within our team is unmatched everyone wants each other to succeed and prosper!”

#EDST

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by EDST 📲 on July 15, 2021 tagging @ram.b__. May be an image of 1 person, sitting and indoor.

node.text:
Team Member Highlight: 

@ram.b__ is an up & coming artist who is absolutely killing it on the team! Let’s show him some love 🔥 

He says, “The beauty of EDST is that it has ALL resources in one company full of like-minded individuals that want to become greater! EDST has made my true plan of working from home and becoming my own boss come to fruition and for that, I won’t stop grinding to become the G.O.A.T🙏🏽” 

#EDST

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by EDST 📲 on July 14, 2021 tagging @epthedreamer23. May be an image of 1 person and sky.

node.text:
Team Member Highlight: 

@epthedreamer23  is a rapper, songwriter, producer and audio engineer working for paramount recording group in Los Angeles. Also working with EDST to level up himself and his clients! 

He says, “When I first started with EDST, my audience wasn’t very engaging and it was hard to get people interested in my music. EDST has taught and helped me get my engagement up while also providing value for a reliable fanbase. I also love the daily scheduled calls EDST has that educates it’s affiliates on investment, techniques of growth, and ways to stand out in the community 🔥” 

#EDST

#EDST
